{"id":"entities/peru","title":"Peru","type":"entities","html":"<h1>Peru</h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Yahir's first <strong>major solo international trip</strong> (Aug 2021), planned obsessively across July 2021 todos and prep notes. Peru is the <strong>prequel to all later off-the-beaten-path travel</strong> — <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/machu-picchu\">machu picchu</a> hiked instead of ticketed, the <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/lima\">Lima</a>→<a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/cusco\">Cusco</a> 20+ hour bus ride, vegetarian-drive packing tactics. Sets the template for <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/jordan\">Jordan</a> (2023), <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/india\">India</a>+<a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/nepal\">Nepal</a> (2024), <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"concepts/china-chapter\">China</a> (2024-25).</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2>Chronology</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>2021-07-28</strong> — <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"summaries/2021-07-28-vegetarian-drive-todos\">vegetarian drive todos</a> include first Peru-prep mentions</li>\n<li><strong>2021-08-03</strong> — <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"summaries/2021-08-03-kira-ford-mentor-intro\">Kira / Ford mentor intro</a> — frames the trip in scholarship-narrative terms</li>\n<li><strong>2021-08-15</strong> — <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"summaries/2021-08-15-kings-of-leon-listening-list\">Kings of Leon listening list</a> for the trip</li>\n<li><strong>2021-08-21</strong> — <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"summaries/2021-08-21-pre-peru-packing-list\">pre Peru packing list</a></li>\n<li><strong>2021-08-24</strong> — <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"summaries/2021-08-24-jann-people-list\">Jann people list</a> (debrief contacts)</li>\n<li><strong>2021-08-26</strong> — <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"summaries/2021-08-26-bus-ride-to-cusco\">bus ride to Cusco</a> — captured live or just-after, the 20+ hour bus</li>\n<li><strong>2021-08-31</strong> — <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"summaries/2021-08-31-seize-the-day-machu-picchu-prep\">seize the day, Machu Picchu prep</a></li>\n<li><strong>2024-08-14</strong> — <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"summaries/2024-08-14-travel-occurrences\">travel occurrences</a> — retrospective gloss naming the 25-mile MP walk</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Why it matters in the graph</h2>\n<p>Peru is where the <strong>finesse-the-route move</strong> first appears as Yahir's signature travel posture — bypass the official ticketed Machu Picchu entry, walk 25 miles of train tracks instead. This becomes the recurring move: <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/petra\">petra</a> off-trail (Jordan, 2023), <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/annapurna-base-camp-trek\">ABC trek</a> (Nepal, 2024). It's also pre-<a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"concepts/china-chapter\">China chapter</a> proof that Yahir would survive long-form discomfort for narrative payoff.</p>\n<h2>Source summaries</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"summaries/2021-07-28-vegetarian-drive-todos\">2021 07 28 vegetarian drive todos</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"summaries/2021-07-29-LIMA-CUSCO\">2021 07 29 LIMA CUSCO</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"summaries/2021-08-03-kira-ford-mentor-intro\">2021 08 03 kira ford mentor intro</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"summaries/2021-08-15-kings-of-leon-listening-list\">2021 08 15 kings of leon listening list</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"summaries/2021-08-21-pre-peru-packing-list\">2021 08 21 pre peru packing list</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"summaries/2021-08-24-jann-people-list\">2021 08 24 jann people list</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"summaries/2021-08-26-bus-ride-to-cusco\">2021 08 26 bus ride to cusco</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"summaries/2021-08-31-seize-the-day-machu-picchu-prep\">2021 08 31 seize the day machu picchu prep</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"summaries/2024-08-14-travel-occurrences\">2024 08 14 travel occurrences</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"summaries/2025-07-12-good-traits\">2025 07 12 good traits</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"summaries/2019-09-11-research-vacations-on-chile\">2019 09 11 research vacations on chile</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Connections</h2>\n<p><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/machu-picchu\">machu picchu</a> · <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/lima\">lima</a> · <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/cusco\">cusco</a> · <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/jann\">jann</a> · <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/ford-family-foundation\">ford family foundation</a> · <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"concepts/six-month-adventure-creed\">six month adventure creed</a> · <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"concepts/non-negotiables-for-traveling\">non negotiables for traveling</a> · <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/jordan\">jordan</a> · <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/india\">india</a> · <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/nepal\">nepal</a> · <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"concepts/china-chapter\">china chapter</a></p>\n","related":[{"id":"summaries/2021-08-24-jann-people-list","label":"'Jann' people list — Aug 24 2021 (souvenirs?)"},{"id":"summaries/2021-08-31-seize-the-day-machu-picchu-prep","label":"'Seize the day' — Machu Picchu trip prep, Aug 31 2021"},{"id":"unresolved/2021-07","label":"2021 07"},{"id":"entities/annapurna-base-camp-trek","label":"Annapurna Base Camp Trek"},{"id":"summaries/2021-08-26-bus-ride-to-cusco","label":"Bus ride to Cusco — Lima-to-Cusco trip prep"},{"id":"concepts/china-chapter","label":"China Chapter"},{"id":"entities/cusco","label":"Cusco"},{"id":"summaries/2024-10-13-Davids-suicide","label":"David's suicide (Oct 13 2024) — grief letter, two days"},{"id":"entities/ford-family-foundation","label":"Ford Family Foundation"},{"id":"summaries/2025-07-12-good-traits","label":"Good traits — Jul 2025 self-inventory"},{"id":"entities/india","label":"India"},{"id":"entities/jann","label":"Jann"},{"id":"entities/jordan","label":"Jordan"},{"id":"summaries/2021-08-15-kings-of-leon-listening-list","label":"Kings of Leon — Aug 2021 listening list"},{"id":"summaries/2021-08-03-kira-ford-mentor-intro","label":"Kira Ford-mentor intro — Peru-prep todos + chiropractor leads"},{"id":"entities/lima","label":"Lima"},{"id":"summaries/2021-07-29-LIMA-CUSCO","label":"Lima / Cusco — first-ever international trip planning, with Dave"},{"id":"entities/machu-picchu","label":"Machu Picchu"},{"id":"entities/nepal","label":"Nepal"},{"id":"concepts/non-negotiables-for-traveling","label":"Non-Negotiables for Traveling"},{"id":"concepts/peru-prep-2021","label":"Peru-prep 2021"},{"id":"entities/petra","label":"Petra"},{"id":"summaries/2021-08-21-pre-peru-packing-list","label":"Pre-Peru packing list — Aug 2021"},{"id":"summaries/2019-09-11-research-vacations-on-chile","label":"Research vacations in Chile / school / Laura Williams"},{"id":"concepts/six-month-adventure-creed","label":"Six Month Adventure Creed"},{"id":"summaries/2024-08-14-travel-occurrences","label":"Travel Occurrences — pre-China mishaps catalog"},{"id":"summaries/2021-07-28-vegetarian-drive-todos","label":"What is your drive to continue vegetarian — July 2021 todos"}]}
